node.text:
I know it’s definitely different for her to get a Father’s Day gift but there is nothing ordinary about our love. I had never gotten the pleasure or the honor to meet my baby’s Dad, Mr. Jesse A. Dupart. I hear so much about him, how loving, brilliant and hard working he was and how she is the spitting image of him. She lights up when she speaks of him. I just wanted a moment to let her know that I am so grateful to him for giving me the greatest gift I’ve ever gotten…HER. 
❤️ @darealbbjudy ❤️ Thank you Pa🙏🏽#sosoblessed #HappyheavenlyFathersDay
